Responsible Social Media Use (Checklist)

Do’s:

Think twice before posting anything online
Keep your personal details private and secure
Be respectful while commenting or replying to others
Check if information is true before sharing it
Go through your privacy settings once in a while

Don’ts:

Don’t spread rumors or fake news
Don’t post anything offensive or hurtful
Don’t share too much personal information publicly
Don’t get involved in unnecessary online fights
Don’t spend too much time scrolling endlessly
